Quote: EHOA is the Vocative or form of addressand means O FRIEND. It is sufficient. Tosay "Dear O Friend" sounds queer. To cutthe O out before friend, you must dropthe E before Hoa, and then you would get"Dear Hoa," which sounds rotten.
